{"tid":2425620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大生靜坐 張翔派糖水縮沙","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T12:54:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c13e0fedb8cb720d77bc65339ad72578b06c637e","tid":2425620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210227/N5DXZU3K3FFRHE2QRSSNO7UNNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210227%2FN5DXZU3K3FFRHE2QRSSNO7UNNE%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=2ba116da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210227%2FN5DXZU3K3FFRHE2QRSSNO7UNNE%2F&h=a302025b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210227/N5DXZU3K3FFRHE2QRSSNO7UNNE/</a><br />\n<br />\n港大生靜坐 張翔派糖水縮沙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/75hBOLHCtMOZLKpG3TAJfkUk5Hg=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/THHNTKYJ5JAR7HCZASZRXGRUOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F75hBOLHCtMOZLKpG3TAJfkUk5Hg%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTHHNTKYJ5JAR7HCZASZRXGRUOY.jpg&h=7c65110e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一批港大學生昨在宿舍外靜坐抗議，港大副校長Ian Holliday（穿西裝者）派發糖水後離開舍堂。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日是正月十五元宵，港大校長張翔原定到訪港大四個宿舍向學生派發糖水。有宿生發起靜坐及杯葛行動，抗議校方在副校長任命等議題上一意孤行、漠視學生意見。張翔卻臨陣退縮沒有現身，派糖水由副校長及學生事務長代勞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n副校代勞 稱張有其他事務<br />\n<br />\n港大副校長Ian Holliday及學生事務長謝樹基傍晚約六時到達港大第二舍堂村。李兆基堂約50名穿黑衣黑褲的學生在宿舍大堂門外靜坐，並舉起寫有「無理解僱戴副教授」、「意圖修改院長遴選指引」、「校委會專行獨斷」、「摧毀港大百年基業」等標語，大堂玻璃門亦貼上「正視學生訴求」等字句，惟Ian Holliday等人未有被阻止進入宿舍大堂。<br />\n<br />\n三間舍堂早前向宿生發電郵，校長張翔及副校長Ian Holliday計劃昨午六時前往宿舍派發糖不甩，送上元宵節祝福。三個宿生會期後刊出聯合聲明，呼籲同學杯葛活動。有非本地學生在大堂等候，結果張翔沒有現身。<br />\n<br />\n港大副校長Ian Holliday及。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n謝樹基表示中大與。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於張翔臨陣退縮，Holliday解釋，他「有其他事務在身」（other engagements）。<br />\n<br />\n參與行動的梁同學表示，靜坐是希望以和平理性的方式向校方傳達學生的聲音，但是張翔最終缺席令人感到非常失望，「睇得出佢唔願意面對學生，知道學生有行動之後就選擇龜縮，非常之唔尊重！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5-lG0xijLHkUPpTHjh2KhJ1Cnno=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YRU4SQDQUZGHJCCIFJLZSPXSJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5-lG0xijLHkUPpTHjh2KhJ1Cnno%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYRU4SQDQUZGHJCCIFJLZSPXSJI.jpg&h=2283c41b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■張翔遭學生狙擊杯葛，未有現身派糖水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wj4s6lasxRoyM6xjxXFxW5lfqM8=/721x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R36ZFWXHLFDD5FNGIFXCANSSFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwj4s6lasxRoyM6xjxXFxW5lfqM8%3D%2F721x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR36ZFWXHLFDD5FNGIFXCANSSFI.jpg&h=57c0e744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大校長張翔"},{"pid":"1e4292a053d2841660beda026e992ead2713d642","tid":2425620,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"聲大大，冇糖水派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}